# EasyFrames Frontend - Project Rules

## Styles

### Typography

#### Fonts
- **Primary Heading Font**: `Playfair Display` (serif) - Use class `font-playfair` for all main headings, section titles, and hero text
- **Body/UI Font**: `Inter` (sans-serif) - Use class `font-inter` for all body text, buttons, descriptions, and UI elements
- **Font Variables**: 
  - `--font-playfair` for Playfair Display
  - `--font-inter` for Inter

#### Font Sizes by Section

**Hero Section:**
- Main heading: `text-4xl sm:text-5xl lg:text-6xl xl:text-6xl` with `font-bold` and `font-playfair`
- Subtitle/description: `text-base lg:text-base` with `font-inter`
- CTA buttons: `text-base` with `font-semibold` and `font-inter`

**Section Headings:**
- Large section titles: `text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl xl:text-5xl` with `font-bold` and `font-playfair`
- Medium section titles: `text-2xl sm:text-3xl lg:text-4xl xl:text-5xl` with `font-bold` and `font-playfair`
- Small section titles: `text-lg sm:text-xl md:text-2xl lg:text-3xl` with `font-bold` and `font-playfair`

**Body Text:**
- Large body: `text-base md:text-lg lg:text-xl` with `font-inter`
- Regular body: `text-sm sm:text-base md:text-base` with `font-inter`
- Small body: `text-xs sm:text-sm` with `font-inter`

**Product Cards:**
- Product title: `text-sm sm:text-base md:text-lg` with `font-semibold` or `font-bold` and `font-inter`
- Price: `text-lg md:text-xl md:text-2xl` with `font-bold` and `font-inter`
- Description: `text-xs sm:text-sm` with `font-inter`

**Navigation:**
- Logo: `text-xl lg:text-2xl` with `font-bold` and `font-playfair`
- Nav items: `text-base` with `font-medium` and `font-inter`

**Buttons:**
- Primary buttons: `text-base` with `font-semibold` and `font-inter`
- Secondary buttons: `text-sm sm:text-base` with `font-medium` and `font-inter`

### Color Palette

#### Primary Colors
- **Dark Slate/Gray**: `slate-900`, `slate-800`, `slate-700` - Use for primary backgrounds, buttons, and dark elements
- **Blue Accents**: `blue-900`, `blue-600`, `blue-500`, `blue-400`, `blue-300` - Use for accents, hover states, and highlights
- **Background Colors**: 
  - Light mode: `bg-gray-50`, `bg-white`
  - Dark mode: `bg-gray-900`, `bg-gray-800`

#### Text Colors
- **Primary Text**: 
  - Light mode: `text-gray-900`, `text-slate-900`
  - Dark mode: `text-gray-100`, `text-white`
- **Secondary Text**: 
  - Light mode: `text-gray-600`, `text-gray-500`
  - Dark mode: `text-gray-400`, `text-gray-300`
- **Accent Text**: `text-blue-600`, `text-blue-500`, `text-blue-400`, `text-blue-300`

#### Border Colors
- **Default Borders**: 
  - Light mode: `border-gray-200`, `border-gray-300`
  - Dark mode: `border-gray-700`, `border-gray-800`
- **Hover Borders**: `border-slate-900`, `border-blue-500`, `border-blue-600`
- **Active Borders**: `border-blue-500`, `border-blue-600`

#### Background Gradients
- **Hero/CTA Gradients**: `bg-gradient-to-br from-slate-900 via-blue-900 to-slate-800`
- **Text Gradients**: `bg-gradient-to-r from-gray-900 to-blue-900` or `from-blue-900 to-gray-900` with `bg-clip-text text-transparent`

### Spacing & Layout

#### Container
- **Max Width**: `max-w-7xl mx-auto` for main containers
- **Padding**: `px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8` for horizontal padding
- **Vertical Padding**: `py-12`, `py-16`, `py-20` for sections

#### Gaps & Spacing
- **Section Gaps**: `gap-4 md:gap-6 lg:gap-8`
- **Card Gaps**: `gap-3 sm:gap-4`
- **Element Gaps**: `space-y-3 sm:space-y-4 md:space-y-6`
- **Section Margins**: `mt-16`, `mb-16` for section separation

#### Border Radius
- **Cards**: `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`
- **Buttons**: `rounded-full` or `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`
- **Images**: `rounded-lg`, `rounded-xl`, or `rounded-2xl`
- **Large Sections**: `rounded-2xl` or `rounded-3xl`

### Component Styling Patterns

#### Cards
- Background: `bg-white dark:bg-gray-900` or `bg-white dark:bg-gray-800`
- Border: `border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700` or `border-0`
- Shadow: `shadow-md hover:shadow-xl` or `shadow-lg hover:shadow-2xl`
- Hover: `transform hover:-translate-y-1` or `hover:scale-105`
- Border radius: `rounded-xl` or `rounded-2xl`
- Padding: `p-4 md:p-6`

#### Buttons
- **Primary Button**: 
  - `bg-slate-900 hover:bg-blue-900 text-white`
  - `rounded-full` or `rounded-xl`
  - `px-8 py-4` or `px-6 py-3`
  - `font-semibold` with `font-inter`
  - `shadow-xl hover:shadow-2xl`
  - `transform hover:scale-105 transition-all duration-200`
- **Secondary/Outline Button**:
  - `border-2 border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600`
  - `hover:border-slate-900 dark:hover:border-white`
  - `text-slate-900 dark:text-white`
  - `hover:bg-slate-900 dark:hover:bg-white hover:text-white dark:hover:text-slate-900`
  - `rounded-full` or `rounded-xl`
  - `font-semibold` with `font-inter`

#### Sections
- Background: `bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900` or `bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-800`
- Container: `container mx-auto max-w-7xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8`
- Spacing: `py-12 md:py-16 lg:py-20`

#### Product Cards
- Image: `w-full h-64 md:h-72 lg:h-80 object-cover`
- Hover effect: `group-hover:scale-110 transition-transform duration-700`
- Overlay: `bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-black/20 to-transparent`
- Badge: `bg-slate-900 text-white px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-xs font-bold`

#### Form Elements
- Input: `border-gray-300 dark:border-gray-600 bg-white dark:bg-gray-800`
- Focus: `focus:border-slate-800 dark:focus:border-slate-300 focus:ring-2 focus:ring-slate-800/20`
- Height: `h-11` for inputs
- Border radius: `rounded-lg`

### Responsive Breakpoints

Always use responsive classes with the following breakpoints:
- **Mobile (default)**: Base styles without prefix
- **Small (sm:)**: `640px+` - Use for tablets
- **Medium (md:)**: `768px+` - Use for small desktops
- **Large (lg:)**: `1024px+` - Use for desktops
- **Extra Large (xl:)**: `1280px+` - Use for large screens

### Dark Mode Support

Always include dark mode variants for:
- Backgrounds: `bg-white dark:bg-gray-900`
- Text: `text-gray-900 dark:text-white`
- Borders: `border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700`
- Use `dark:` prefix for all dark mode styles

### Animation & Transitions

- **Hover Transitions**: `transition-all duration-200` or `duration-300`
- **Transform on Hover**: `transform hover:scale-105` or `hover:-translate-y-1`
- **Shadow Transitions**: `shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl` or `hover:shadow-2xl`
- **Color Transitions**: Always include `transition-colors duration-200`

### Special Effects

- **Gradient Borders**: Use `.glow-border` class for animated gradient borders
- **Backdrop Blur**: `backdrop-blur-sm` or `backdrop-blur-xl` for glass effects
- **Gradient Overlays**: `bg-gradient-to-t from-black/60 via-black/20 to-transparent` for image overlays

### Icon Sizes

- **Small Icons**: `w-4 h-4` or `w-5 h-5`
- **Medium Icons**: `w-5 h-5` or `w-6 h-6`
- **Large Icons**: `w-8 h-8` or `w-10 h-10`
- Use Lucide React icons consistently

